data.description: Welcome to Haciendas Del Norte . This Winton  resale home offers 3  bedrooms , 2 bathrooms along with a sunken living room and a nice  dining room . The kitchen has plenty of space with  an island. This home also features a sunroom,  double car garage ,2 fire places,  and not to mention it is situated on a 3 acre lot. This property comes with a storage shed, stables and fencing in the back perimeter of the property. If you like privacy, views, tranquility, and being away from the city, Haciendas Del Norte should be part of your checklist.
